00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:38.040
Second, futures thinking.

00:07:38.680 --> 00:07:40.656
When we think about the future,

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:41.920
10, 15 years out,

00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:44.778
give me a vision of what the future is.

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:48.656
You don't have to give it to me,
but think in your head.

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:50.816
And what you're probably going to see

00:07:50.840 --> 00:07:52.656
is the dominant cultural lens

00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:55.736
that dominates our thinking
about the future right now:

00:07:55.760 --> 00:07:56.960
technology.

00:07:57.840 --> 00:07:59.576
So when we think about the problems,

00:07:59.600 --> 00:08:01.776
we always put it through
a technological lens,